description:
IT&#39;S ZOMBIES VS VAMPIRES&mdash;WITH HUMANS CAUGHT IN THE CROSSFIRE&mdash;
AS THE LEGENDARY GEORGE ROMERO UNLEASHES HIS NEXT UNDEAD EPIC!




<ul><li>Welcome to New York years after the eruption of an undead plague&mdash;a city not only teeming with roaming zombies, but also ruled by vampires!</li><li>Meanwhile, in the pit of the bloody Circus Maximus, can anything stop the unchained fury of the zombie gladiator known as Zanzibar?</li><li>Plus: It&#39;s a terrorizing team-up in variant cover form when the Zombie Godfather George Romero unites with the Zombie King Arthur Suydam!</li></ul>

